data.description: One of a kind! Two living areas! A 1920's Home that is unique and in a location for both residential and or office use! With original hardwood floors, glass knobs and brass hardware- this home has a lot of architectural design that is hard to find in this pristine condition. The kitchen has been remodeled with stainless steel appliances and a stainless farmhouse sink. With an additional efficiency living area at the back of the home with a separate entrance- can be used  for an airbnb or additional income or a mother in law suite!  There is an outdoor entertainment space complete with a, bar, and outdoor lighting - perfect for the Florida lifestyle! This home had a new roof installed in September 2023. Located close to Historic downtown Eustis as well as a short drive to Mount Dora and Lake Eustis.
